ImageDataLoaders.from_csv: column name containing filenames with full paths
ImageDataLoaders.from_csv: column name containing lables, if space is present, then they will be considerd mutliple lables

Column name containing boolean whether to create gradCAM images for given rows
Pixel size to which the images should be resized in x y dimensions, must be at least 224
Resize class method: squish, pad, crop
Resize class  and aug_transform pad_mode: zeros, border, reflection
aug_transforms: should horizontal flip be done
aug_transforms: should verticle flip be done
aug_transforms: maximum rotation on image in degrees
aug_transforms: zoom range minimum
aug_transforms: zoom range maximum
aug_transforms: degree of warp
aug_transforms: prbability of affine (above) transformations
aug_transforms: max change in lighting

String of model architexture that is used by Learner, can be fastai supported from: https://pytorch.org/vision/stable/models.html
To which parameter group to freeze the model: -1 head, conventional freeze(), 0 unfreeze all, other int
Callbacks, additional functionalities evaluated on each epoch, arguments are given here, if you wish to use arguments defined in this document then use att_dic['arg'] where arg is a valid var_name
Learner: loss function, see Loss Functions, if None then infeered from outcome type
Learner: optimalization function, see Optimizers
fit_one_cycle: momentums used

Learning strategy, currently supported: "discriminative" using min and max of suggest_funcs, "sequential" running n_epoch on each suggest_funcs result in order they are provided
